<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Blocked - Medical Articles</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        .blocked-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a24 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .blocked-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .blocked-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: #ff6b6b;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="blocked-container">
        <div class="blocked-card">
            <i class="fas fa-ban blocked-icon"></i>
            <h1 class="mb-3">Account Blocked</h1>
            <p class="text-muted mb-4">
                Your account has been temporarily blocked due to a violation of our community guidelines. 
                This action was taken to ensure the safety and quality of our platform.
            </p>
            <div class="alert alert-info mb-4">
                <h6 class="mb-2">
                    <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                    What happens now?
                </h6>
                <ul class="text-start mb-0">
                    <li>Your account access has been suspended</li>
                    <li>You cannot create or edit articles</li>
                    <li>Your existing content may be under review</li>
                    <li>This action was reviewed by our moderation team</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="mb-2">
                    <strong>Need to appeal this decision?</strong>
                </p>
                <p class="text-muted small">
                    If you believe this action was taken in error, please contact our support team 
                    with your account details and a brief explanation.
                </p>
            </div>
            <a href="mailto:support@tabeeb.email" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg me-2">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>
                Contact Support
            </a>
            <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg">
                <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-2"></i>
                Try Again
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>